shortDescription: Phoebe and Paige attempt to rescue Chris and Leo but find themselves battling their evil counterparts.

title: A Call To Arms
subtitle: A Call To Arms
shortDescription: After Leo and Piper inadvertently receive the powers of Hindu gods, Phoebe and Paige must keep them from consummating their love in order to save the universe.

title: Oh My Goddess, Part 2
shortDescription: Leo turns the sisters into Greek goddesses so they will be able to vanquish mythic giants.
description: Now all-powerful goddesses, the Charmed Ones must try to not be seduced by their new powers and stay focused on vanquishing the Titans before the Titans can destroy all the whitelighters and elders. Meanwhile, Leo must decide whether to become an elder or remain with his family.

title: Used Karma
subtitle: Used Karma
shortDescription: Phoebe's boyfriend leaves her after learning she, Paige and Piper are actually witches; Richard tries to free himself of the family's karma.

title: The Legend of Sleepy Halliwell
subtitle: The Legend of Sleepy Halliwell
shortDescription: Leo's mentor, Gideon, wants to find out who cast the spell of darkness over the school and conjured the headless horseman who has been beheading the teachers; Phoebe goes on a vision quest.

title: I Dream of Phoebe
subtitle: I Dream of Phoebe
shortDescription: The charmed ones get wishful when a genie named Jinny is freed from her bottle by Phoebe, who is then tricked into taking her place.

title: Hyde School Reunion
subtitle: Hyde School Reunion
shortDescription: Phoebe accidentally casts a spell on herself that allows her wild teenage personality to take over; Piper asks her father to find out why Chris is avoiding her.

title: Spin City
subtitle: Spin City
shortDescription: The Spider Demon kidnaps and cocoons Piper and turns Chris into a spider.

title: Crimes and Witch-Demeanors
subtitle: Crimes and Witch-Demeanors
shortDescription: When the Charmed Ones are caught on tape using their powers, the Cleaners cover up the situation by framing Darryl as a murderer and sending him to death row.

title: Witch Wars
subtitle: Witch Wars
